### Commands

```bash
# Lint
golangci-lint run ./...

# Test with race detection
go test -race ./...

# Test with coverage
go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./...
go tool cover -func=coverage.out

# Run all checks before committing
golangci-lint run ./... && go test -race -coverprofile=coverage.out ./...
```

